	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You thrust both of your hands into the ground, and sing a short paean to the primal forest. As your words echo and fade, plants in a wide radius are vitalized and grow rapidly as the land is enriched.</em></p><p><strong>Utility</strong></p><ul><li><p>All normal plants become thick and overgrown. Any space that was within 5 ft. of a &amp;reference[plant] is now covered in plant life and counts as &amp;reference[difficult terrain]. You can exclude one or more areas of any size within the spell's area from being affected.</p></li><li><p>The plants double in volume, and yield twice the food or other produce when harvested, if applicable.</p></li><li><p>If these plants are affected by this spell a second time in a growing season, the food or produce spoils, but the plants still grow and create more &amp;reference[difficult terrain].</p></li></ul>",
			"chat": ""
		},
